     * @notice Gets required margin for squeeth
     * RequiredMargin_{squeeth}
     * = max((1-Î±) * S * |WeightDelta_{sqeeth}-Î± * S * gamma|, (1+Î±) * S * |WeightDelta_{sqeeth}+Î± * S * gamma|)
